    <value>This example shows that when we have a long operation the program is bussy and can't do other thing, the program is frozen and does not respond even to our hovering on a button or pressing the buttons.
If we ask for another operation the click is queued and will run only after the long operation finised to run

When we operate the "long operation" in adiffrent thread, we can use another thread (in this examople it's the main thread) to run the 'other operation' in the meanwhile.

p.s. The UI belongs to the main thread</value>
